title: IAA Tonight | Dan Snyder Possibly Selling the Washington Commanders?
description: Washington Commanders owners Dan and Tanya Snyder have hired Bank of America Securities to "consider potential transactions," including the potential sale of the franchise. LeSean "Shady McCoy, Adam "Pacman" Jones, and Leger Douzable discuss the franchise possibly changing owners, and if the Miami Dolphins put themselves in Super Bowl contention with the addition of Bradley Chubb.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, LeSean McCoy, Adam Pacman Jones)
